# Persistent Agent Rules (IDE Agents)

- Use FastAPI + SQLAlchemy + Pydantic patterns already documented in this repository.
- Keep React/TypeScript components strongly typed and form logic based on React Hook Form.
- Use Recharts wrappers from shared UI packages where available.
- Preserve auditability for metabolic computations with formula versioning metadata.
- For Dataverse connectivity, route through MCP-compatible specs in `specs/`.
